info.description:
This package is a basic wrapper for qsiprep that generates the appropriate
Docker commands, providing an intuitive interface to running the qsiprep
workflow in a Docker environment.
info.name: qsiprep-container
info.summary: qsiprep is a non-DTI diffusion-weighted image pre-processing pipeline that is designed to provide an easily accessible, state-of-the-art interface that is robust to differences in scan acquisition protocols and that requires minimal user input, while providing easily interpretable and comprehensive error and output reporting.
